Diagram 1 — Keras Module View (Static Dependency Structure)

Diagram Purpose & Meaning:
This diagram presents the high-level static dependency structure of Keras.
It shows how the main architectural subsystems relate through directed dependencies.

Key relationships shown:
- models depends on layers
- models depends on optimizers
- models depends on losses
- layers depends on backend
- optimizers depends on backend
